            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-6">
                <p id="developer-signature" style="float: right;"><br><strong>Developed by University of Ghana Information Technology Directorate(UGITD)</strong><br><br></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>